Revision history for Perl module Directory::Diff

0.09 2025-05-13

- Fix verbose flag in ls_dir
- Make ls_dir not fail on a directory called "0"
- Check for errors in return values
- Documentation

0.08 2018-11-17

- Removed unused testing routines "default_dir_only" and "default_diff"
- Additional tests for DD::Copy

0.07 2017-10-25

- Restore accidentally removed dependence on mkpath in File::Copy

0.06 2017-10-14

- Improved documentation for Directory::Diff::Copy

0.05 2016-08-23

- Copy permissions when files are copied

0.04 2016-02-11

- Fix broken test
- More documentation improvements

0.03 2016-02-11

- Documentation improvements

0.02 2016-02-05

- Fixed documentation errors
- Fixed test script for Windows

0.01 2016-02-04

- Initial version

